<p><strong>东野圭吾悬疑舞台剧《虚无的十字架》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200909/7ecde5bac32241b7a21a106a2eebf10d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
